Privacy Policy
1. Information Collection
Our weather app may collect information about your location to provide accurate weather forecasts. We do not associate your location information with personally identifiable information. In addition, we may collect anonymised usage data to improve the functionality and performance of the application.
2. Use of Information
The information we collect will only be used to provide weather forecasts and to improve the functionality and performance of the application. We will not use your information for other purposes and will not share it with any third party organization or individual.
3. Information security
We will take reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use or disclosure.
4. Updates to our Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect our business needs and legal requirements. After updating the Privacy policy, we will update it on this page, and you can view the latest version on the Privacy Policy page.
5. Contact us
If you have any questions or comments about our privacy policy, you can contact us at:wangyudev@163.com. We will respond to your questions and address your concerns as soon as possible.